1892, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 500511, "username": "albert0yyyy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/albert0yyyy", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02c953716ffd48dab60c9d9c1960fe37?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02c953716ffd48dab60c9d9c1960fe37?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02c953716ffd48dab60c9d9c1960fe37?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1595497120, "last_modified": 1715862173}, "last_reply_by": "wupher", "last_touched": 1719457428, "title": "开车上班第一天，心好累", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1052962", "created": 1719450941, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前坐地铁，是身体累，经常没位置，要站着。然后要挤，但是挤上去就好了。\r\n\r\n今天试试开车上班，其实最后发现还是比坐地铁快很多。但是就是心累，一个因为我是司机，我得一直注意路况。然后就是堵车，我刚刚也说了再堵总时间也还是快的，但是就有一种不畅快的感觉，地铁轰隆隆的往前开，就很畅快，很舒服 。\r\n\r\n老哥你们说习惯是不是就好了？", "content_rendered": "<p>之前坐地铁，是身体累，经常没位置，要站着。然后要挤，但是挤上去就好了。</p>\n<p>今天试试开车上班，其实最后发现还是比坐地铁快很多。但是就是心累，一个因为我是司机，我得一直注意路况。然后就是堵车，我刚刚也说了再堵总时间也还是快的，但是就有一种不畅快的感觉，地铁轰隆隆的往前开，就很畅快，很舒服 。</p>\n<p>老哥你们说习惯是不是就好了？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719450941, "replies": 62, "id": 1052962}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 220331, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4204, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 645152, "username": "wyzane", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wyzane", "website": "blog.wangzan.cc", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mi